OL,3,CReal Madrid make initial approach to
OL,4,CLiverpool for Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FIt's understood that Real Madrid have
OL,7,Fmade an initial approach to Liverpool
OL,8,Fover signing Trent Alexander-Arnold in
OL,9,Ftime for the Club World Cup.
OL,11,FAlexander-Arnold announced on Monday
OL,12,Fmorning, just over a week after
OL,13,Fhelping the Reds secure a 20th English
OL,14,Ftitle, that he would be leaving his
OL,15,Fboyhood club on a free transfer in the
OL,16,Fsummer.
OL,18,FMadrid have long been touted as his
OL,19,Flikeliest destination and it is
OL,20,Funderstood contact has been made to
OL,21,Fhasten his arrival at the Bernabeu.
