OL,3,CReal Madrid make initial approach to
OL,4,CLiverpool for Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FThe 26-year-old's deal at Anfield
OL,7,Fexpires officially on June 30, but the
OL,8,FSpanish club would like to have him in
OL,9,Fthe squad for the summer tournament in
OL,10,Fthe United States. They have group
OL,11,Fgames on June 18, 22 and 26.
OL,13,FIt is likely a fee would need to be
OL,14,Fagreed to persuade Liverpool to do
OL,15,Fbusiness, but there is no indication
OL,16,Fyet as to whether they are prepared to
OL,17,Fpush things forward.
