OL,3,CReal Madrid make initial approach to
OL,4,CLiverpool for Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FAlexander-Arnold broke the news, which
OL,7,Fhas been anticipated ever since Real
OL,8,Fwere strongly linked with the England
OL,9,Finternational in January, in an
OL,10,Femotional post on social media.
OL,12,F"After 20 years at Liverpool Football
OL,13,FClub, now is the time for me to
OL,14,Fconfirm that I will be leaving at the
OL,15,Fend of the season," he wrote on X.
