OL,3,CReal Madrid make initial approach to
OL,4,CLiverpool for Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,F"This is easily the hardest decision
OL,7,FI've ever made in my life. I know many
OL,8,Fof you have wondered why or been
OL,9,Ffrustrated that I haven't spoken about
OL,10,Fthis yet, but it was always my
OL,11,Fintention to keep my full focus on the
OL,12,Fteam's best interests, which was
OL,13,Fsecuring No.20.
OL,15,F"This club has been my whole life ` my
OL,16,Fwhole world ` for 20 years. I will
OL,17,Fforever be in debt to you all. My love
OL,18,Ffor this club will never die."
