OL,3,CReal Madrid make initial approach to
OL,4,CLiverpool for Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FIt is understood Alexander-Arnold
OL,7,Fwould have become the highest-paid
OL,8,Ffull-back in the Premier League had he
OL,9,Faccepted Liverpool's improved terms.
OL,11,FConversations with the player's agent
OL,12,Fbegan before Arne Slot arrived as head
OL,13,Fcoach last summer, but while Mohamed
OL,14,FSalah and Virgil van Dijk did recently
OL,15,Fagree new deals, talks with Alexander-
OL,16,FArnold's camp were less fruitful.
