OL,4,CLiverpool for Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FJamie Carragher, who spent his entire
OL,7,Fcareer at Liverpool, articulated the
OL,8,Fviews of many fans when he suggested
OL,9,FAlexander-Arnold running down his
OL,10,Fcontract would lower his standing with
OL,11,Fthe club's supporters.
OL,13,F"With Monday's statement, the
OL,14,Funconditional support Alexander-Arnold
OL,15,Fenjoyed from the Kop when he was fully
OL,16,Fcommitted to Liverpool has gone," he
OL,17,Fwrote in the Telegraph.
